reviewText: Wonderful course! Thank you for your knowledge and expertise.
Excellent Course. The trainer was awesome and has presented very well
So well put together and just fun to take.  The delivery  was just right and the Instructure was insightful and fun at the same time.

I'm certainly a fan of Dr. Baker.  He has a very affable nature and makes the course enjoyable.  I would highly recommend that you do the optional discussion questions as you get the opportunity to apply what you have learned.  It makes the learning stick and applicable to your organization.  - Thank you, Andrew J Singleton
